nd to govern the day and the night, and to separate the light from the darkness; and God saw that it was good.\n19 There was evening and there was morning, a fourth day.\n20 Then God said, “Let the waters teem with swarms of living creatures, and let birds fly above the earth in the open expanse of the heavens.”"
